*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zcmy_test_80.

DATA : gv_num1 TYPE i,
       gv_num2 TYPE i.

START-OF-SELECTION.

  gv_num1 = 2.
  gv_num2 = 4.

  PERFORM sum.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form sum
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM sum .
  DATA : lv_sum TYPE i.

  lv_sum = gv_num1 + gv_num2.

  PERFORM write USING lv_sum.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form write
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      --> LV_SUM
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM write  USING    p_lv_sum.
  WRITE : TEXT-001 , p_lv_sum.
ENDFORM.
